<div1>
        <head>Epigramma alterum in obtractorem Augustini</head>

<l>
<pb n="0149C"/> <emph>193</emph> Contra Augustinum narratur serpere quidam</l>
<l rend="indent">
<pb n="0150C"/>Scriptor, quem dudum livor adussit edax:</l>
<l>
<pb n="0151A"/> Qui caput obscuris contectum utcumque cavernis</l>
<l rend="indent">Tollere humo miserum perpulit anguiculum.</l> 
<l>Aut hunc fruge sua aequorei pavere Britanni,</l>
<l rend="indent">Aut huic Campano gramine corda tument.</l> 
<l> <emph>195</emph> Quae concepta fovet promat, quae parturit edat;</l>
<l rend="indent">
<pb n="0152A"/>Seu vetere armatur dogmate, sive novo.</l> 
<l>In quoscumque sinus spirarum torqueat orbes,</l>
<l rend="indent">Et fallax multa contegat arte caput;</l>
<l>Currentem attritos super aspidas et basiliscos</l>
<l rend="indent">Declinare senem vipera non poterit.</l> 

</div1>
